'''Special Files''' were records that were ultra-secret in the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Retreating [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial forces]] were ordered to destroy all Special Files they had. The [[Caamas Document]] was one such file.<ref name="Specter">''[[Specter of the Past]]''</ref>

